  "keyFeatures": [
    "6-layer trait-driven architecture (Security, Orchestrator, Memory, Event Bus, Tools, Channels)",
    "Multi-provider LLM support with automatic fallback (Anthropic, OpenAI, DeepSeek, Groq, Gemini, Ollama)",
    "Hybrid memory search combining SQLite FTS5, vector embeddings, and reciprocal rank fusion",
    "Edge-optimized runtime (<5MB binary, <10ms boot, 3.8M messages/sec throughput)",
    "Deny-by-default security with device pairing and per-command authorization",
    "Multi-channel I/O (CLI, TCP, Telegram, MQTT) with round-robin management",
    "Sync and async event bus implementations for realtime event processing",
    "Extensible tool system with sandboxed execution",
    "Cross-platform ARM/x86_64 support with systemd deployment"
  ],
